---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
const { cta_url } = Astro.props;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Unlock the power of manifestation with Vibrational Energy Codes. Elevate your consciousness with sacred geometry, words of power, and vibrant colors.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Vibrational Energy Codes, manifestation, energy codes, sacred geometry, Dr. Masaru Emoto, manifestation journey, positive energy, digital product, abundance, love, health">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Vibrational Energy Codes">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Manifest abundance, love, and health with Vibrational Energy Codes. Infuse intention into every sip of water and elevate your vibration with sacred geometry and words of power.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="/VibrationalEnergyCodes.png">
    <meta property="og:url" content={cta_url}>
    <meta property="og:type" content="book">
    <title>Energy Codes</title>
    <link rel="canonical" href={cta_url}>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 mb-8 mt-12 sm:mt-12 sm:mb-12 sm:px-6 md:mt-32 md:mb-20 xl:mt-23 xl:mb-24">
      <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
        <div class="mb-12 md:max-w-1xl md:mx-auto lg:col-span-8">
          <h1
            class="mt-1 text-5xl tracking-tight leading-16 font-extrabold sm:leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl uppercase"
          ><span class="underline">Energy Codes</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            The <b>Vibrational Energy Codes</b> PDF offers flexibility in using healing codes for manifestation. Unlike traditional books, this digital format allows you to print and use specific codes as needed to infuse intention into your everyday life. Volume 1 includes six powerful codes designed to elevate your manifesting abilities:</p>

          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            <li>Money & Abundance Code</li>
            <li>Freedom & Abundance Code</li>
            <li>Love & Abundance Code</li>
            <li>PURE Money Code</li>
            <li>PURE Love Code</li>
            <li>PURE Energy Code</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            Empower your daily experience by using these codes in versatile applications such as water bottles, fruit baskets, or even under your pillow. Drawing inspiration from sacred geometry and the research of Dr. Masaru Emoto, these codes transform the vibrational frequency of water, making every sip an opportunity for manifestation.</p>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            <b>Why Choose Vibrational Energy Codes:</b></p>

          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            <li>Empower Your Manifesting Abilities</li>
            <li>Infuse Positive Energy into Every Sip</li>
            <li>Versatile Applications for Daily Use</li>
            <li>Inspired by Sacred Geometry and Vibrant Colors</li>
            <li>Elevate Your Consciousness and Daily Experience</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            This is a digital product (PDF), and you will receive an email with download instructions. Digital goods are non-refundable.</p>

            <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
              <div>
                <a
                  href={cta_url}
                  target="_blank"
                  class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base leading-6 rounded-md font-semibold text-white bg-book-theme hover:bg-book-hover focus:outline-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10"
                >
                  Get It Now
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="mt-12 relative sm:max-w-lg sm:mx-auto lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:col-span-4 lg:flex lg:items-center"
        >
          <a class="book-container" href={cta_url}>
            <div class="book">
              <Image
                src="/VibrationalEnergyCodes.png"
                width={300}
                height={600}
                alt="Vibrational Energy Codes PDF Cover"
                format="avif"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
